Aptora - Field Service Management Software














































































 













 





About Us




We’re contractors building software for contractors.
Our mission is to enrich the lives of business owners by providing convenient, profitable, and efficiency driven field service management software tools.
We pride ourselves in designing service management software that is simple in design, easy to use, enables mobility, convenient, and creates value for the business owner.
Contact Us



Aptora understands the difficulties and frustration of finding the perfect software for your company headaches, as well as knowing how important your software is to you.
We are dedicated to making your business life easier through creating and supporting accounting and service management software that eliminates inefficient and annoying business processes.
Aptora achieves this by providing award-winning software to help our clients increase efficiency and profit margins, as well as a constantly connecting our clients to free resources and advice.


Our Products and Services
Aptora is best known for our enterprise level accounting and management software Total Office Manager. We also produce the world’s best flat rate pricing software, Flat Rate Plus. Both of these applications are proven to deliver an immediate return on investment and better our client’s business.
Please take time to view our software or even attend one of our free weekly webinars.
Contact us for more information at (913) 492-9930.

Our Office
Our offices are conveniently located in Lenexa KS just minutes from downtown Kansas City and 35 minutes from Kansas City International airport. Our sister company, RA Tax and Accounting shares the building with Aptora.
Please click here for full contact information.






 











 










 



 







